item.title: Hep please portforward problem
item.dc:creator: @Wet_Dreamss Wet Dreamss
item.description:
@Wet_Dreamss wrote:

[quote=“Dylan 100123, post:3, topic:420448”][quote author=Wet Dreamss link=topic=522996.msg3804564#msg3804564 date=1320349143]

ive portforwarded me rsps but wen i go to canyouseeme.org or try to conect to me server it says it isnt able to so what did i do wrong??

Go to your firewall settings, you can do the simple way: Turn your fire wall completely off

Harder (yet still simple) way: Go to exceptions. Create a new port that matches the one you just made for your server.
If both of these don’t work, go to portforward.com and find your router and just follow its steps ^.^
[/quote]

well turning of me firewall complytly ist good cuz im not protected than
and i used the tutorial from portforward.com and i did at a new port for me rsps
but when i go to canyouseemy.org it still says i can NOT see you[/quote]
Read your pm’s
